{"tid":1433151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［大家冷靜] 開多一個記者會唔代表係大台","createTime":"2019-08-08T11:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T01:47:33.000Z","uid":55257,"like":58,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a277dbf01493663ee013d3b38e539b3bd028d56e","tid":1433151,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:58:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n宜家成場運動好需要一班沉默卻大多數的「和理非」支持，如果佢地「全港反送中大聯席」可以吸引到「和理非」的關注，又能夠彌補勇武派的不足（包括學者的文宣、議員的支援等等），只要大家唔割蓆，一定可以做到互相幫助的力量。佢地有記者會，民間又有記者會，各有各做，何樂而不為？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位緊記：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不分化，不割蓆</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"23bd8848a2261f76ad5bb0238755d5f26b086aea","tid":1433151,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e690e5cbc0d9bc4ce7d35026a742bbb30657d704","tid":1433151,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111e483b8a38a33185a3d95212c9b7a83cbf5601","tid":1433151,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持"},{"pid":"a936a686d6b42d1f054c6c522d7e8930807334a6","tid":1433151,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:01:01.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7575529ab3a81900a02910566547fe968394cc45","tid